This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=5000

Make things clickable, even in vim.

default ones are urls and files , and you can define your own clickable things. 

for example, with additional bundles installed(https://github.com/Rykka/clickable-things),
clicking the 'Bundle "xxx/yyy"' will jump to the '~/.vim/bundle/yyy' directory directly.

.. image :: http://i.imgur.com/9T91tLb.gif

See details in github: https://github.com/Rykka/clickable.vim

